Class VariableBindings

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,List<Object>>

    public class VariableBindings
extends HashMap<String,List<Object>>
    Encapsulates value bindings which are incomplete. This functions as a restriction for further queries by a database request for historical data. In the end these bindings serve to fulfill a join with the final data. Variable names (the keys in this collection) are specified using their plain name e.g., "var1" instead of the SPARQL syntax "?var1" or "$var1".
